The paper deals with the formal verification of control strategies for platoon formation of vehicles, which involves the use of autonomous driving, vehicle-to-vehicle communication, and smart traffic controllers. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), embedded systems (cs.ET), programming languages (cs.PL), and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
